metadata.name: BORN 2 DIE
metadata.description:
This piece was created as a derivative of Terrell Jones 'Born 2 Die' contest for his artwork of Skelliot Deville holding a sacrificial origami lamb.

This piece is to take Skelliot into a different universe, a time of the past. This shows Skelliot with a lamb at the top of a sacrificial ritual site where he has defended himself against adversaries and other obstacles. After facing the struggles to fight his way to the top, his last conflict to face is a decision.

Will he make his sacrifice for all his desires or to let the lamb live a long life?

--

PaleInRed 2022
